---

### 6. **Extensions Boundary Rules**

**Location**: `/private/var/folders/vq/9q38rw0x2455zr_whqcrjbhr0000gn/T/planmode-bench-wt-run-1775467524242-gn0vo7/extensions/AGENTS.md`

