### 12. **Directory Structure Template for New Plugin**

```
extensions/my-channel/
├── package.json                 # Plugin metadata & openclaw config
├── openclaw.plugin.json         # Plugin manifest
├── index.ts                     # Main entry (defineChannelPluginEntry)
├── setup-entry.ts              # Setup-only entry (defineSetupPluginEntry)
├── api.ts                       # Public API barrel (export * from ./src/...)
├── channel-config-api.ts       # Optional: Channel-specific config
├── runtime-api.ts              # SDK re-exports (export * from "openclaw/plugin-sdk/...")
├── src/
│   ├── channel.ts              # ChannelPlugin implementation (createChatChannelPlugin)
│   ├── types.ts                # Account config/resolution types
│   ├── config-schema.ts        # Zod schema for channel config
│   ├── runtime.ts              # Runtime store (createPluginRuntimeStore)
│   ├── accounts.ts             # Account ID listing & resolution
│   ├── setup-surface.ts        # Setup wizard & adapter
│   ├── setup-core.ts           # Core setup logic (if needed)
│   ├── normalize.ts            # Target/ID normalization
│   ├── policy.ts               # Policy resolution (groups, DMs)
│   ├── probe.ts                # Health/connection checking
│   ├── inbound.ts              # Inbound message handling
│   ├── send.ts                 # Outbound message delivery
│   ├── monitor.ts              # Runtime monitoring
│   └── [other domain files]    # Client, protocol, etc.
└── test/
    └── [test files]
```

