### 13. `extensions/pulseboard/src/accounts.ts`

Multi-account resolution following `irc/src/accounts.ts` pattern exactly. Key exports:

- `ResolvedPulseBoardAccount` type: `{ accountId, enabled, name?, configured, serverUrl, apiKey, username, config }`
- `listPulseBoardAccountIds(cfg)` — uses `createAccountListHelpers("pulseboard", { normalizeAccountId })`
- `resolveDefaultPulseBoardAccountId(cfg)`
